          "date": "2016-11-24 12:13:46.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-3392 osd-ldiskfs: handle large file writting gracefully",
        "message": "LU-3392 osd-ldiskfs: handle large file writting gracefully\n\nldiskfs could not handle file size over 16TB, and it could\nnot map physical space for writting in such case, we could\nreturn a too big file errors rather than trigger assertion\nin such case, since this could really happen and it is not\na BUG.\n\nBesides, output fid of affected files in the system log.\n\nSigned-off-by: Wang Shilong <wshilong@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Ia66409a642c761ece0d1937f5c225e54dfff6f71\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
